snippet.title: Zack Snyder Teases FINAL CRISIS | WONDER WOMAN 3 Plot Revealed?
snippet.description:
That Hashtag Show reveals that they may know the early draft plot breakdown for WONDER WOMAN 3 that includes Aquaman team up.  Zack Snyder hides a clue in a Thanksgiving Day post that is revealed to be a book - Absolute Final Crisis.  Is Zack teasing an involvement in an epic project?  Is Zack teasing research for Zack Snyder's Justice League 2 and 3?
